body_html: HP split into 2 companies last year: HP Inc. and Hewlett Packard Enterprise - I'm at Hewlett Packard Enterprise Labs, so we need our own CLA. I've sent the CLA to legal - let me see if I can get a response within a week. Otherwise maybe you will need to do it.
